rows.label: qst201908_msg0001
rows.name: What?! There are that many fools?!

rows.label: qst201908_msg0002
rows.name:
At this rate, we won't be able
to tell which one is Suisui.

rows.label: qst201908_msg0003
rows.name:
Very well. If we catch them
one by one, we will eventually
find the right one!

rows.label: qst201908_msg0004
rows.name: Are you sure that's a good idea...?

rows.label: qst201908_msg0005
rows.name:
It matters not! Action is
all that is required!
